The spatially resolved kinematics pipeline produces a pickle file with name "DESJ2112_r_spatially_resolved_kinematics.pkl."
To access this file, go to the "Spatially-Resolved Kinematics" folder, and you will see it there. You will also need the 
HST WFC3 F140W and F200LP images for this system, which you can access in this Google Drive folder:
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1AgM9qi_REJcq-pWxjm4wkqYecZYvXsWL?usp=sharing
